            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ud/aktuelt/taler_artikler/utenriksministeren/2010/northern_knowledge.html?id=614593" title="">
                        Norway and Russia. Taking Northern Knowledge to the Next Level
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Northern Arctic Federal University, Arkhangelsk, 17 September 2010. </h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 17.09.2010]</p>
                <p>"Developments in the High North must be based on knowledge. This is vital for sustainability and stability. I believe we should build a northern hub of knowledge. The enhanced cooperation between Russian universities and scientific institutions and their Norwegian counterparts is an important part of this", Foreign Minister Støre said in his speech at the Northern Arctic Federal University in Arkhangelsk on 17 September 2010.      </p>
                
                
